# 🧠 Core Laravel Concepts Used

## 📌 MVC Architecture

* Models manage database logic
* Controllers handle application logic
* Views render frontend UI

## 📌 Eloquent Relationships

Used relationships:

* One-to-Many
* Many-to-Many
* BelongsTo
* HasMany

Example:

```php
public function status()
{
    return $this->belongsTo(JobStatus::class);
}
```

## 📌 Form Request Validation

Custom validation classes are used for clean and reusable validation.

```php
$request->validated();
```

## 📌 Database Seeders

Seeders populate default data such as:

* Job Statuses
* Skills

## 📌 Blade Templating

Reusable layouts and components:

```blade
@extends('layouts.app')
@section('content')
```

## 📌 Flash Messages

Used for success and error notifications.

