# 🗄 Database Tables Overview

| Table        | Purpose                       |
| ------------ | ----------------------------- |
| users        | Stores registered users       |
| jobs         | Stores job applications       |
| job_statuses | Stores application statuses   |
| skills       | Stores available skills       |
| job_skill    | Pivot table for jobs & skills |

---

# 🔗 Table Relationships

## User → Jobs

One user can create many jobs.

```text
users.id → jobs.user_id
```

## Job → Status

Each job belongs to one status.

```text
job_statuses.id → jobs.job_status_id
```

## Jobs ↔ Skills

Many-to-Many relationship.

```text
jobs.id ↔ job_skill.job_id
skills.id ↔ job_skill.skill_id
```


